00:41:01,993 --> 00:41:03,017
Murphy.

530
00:41:11,869 --> 00:41:12,996
Suction.

531
00:41:20,078 --> 00:41:22,513
Never forget,
you're the smart one.

532
00:41:23,114 --> 00:41:24,377
You can do anything.

