in medical school.

543
00:42:13,064 --> 00:42:14,623
You're much better than them.

544
00:42:15,066 --> 00:42:16,557
I have a lot to learn from you.

545
00:42:24,008 --> 00:42:25,306
You're very arrogant.

546
00:42:27,245 --> 00:42:29,407
Do you think that helps
you be a good surgeon?

547
00:42:31,315 --> 00:42:32,943
